## Styling & Mobile-First
- Base breakpoint: 375px (iPhone SE).
- Use Tailwind CSS (or CSS Modules if Tailwind not in project).
- Touch targets minimum 44px height per fight row.
- No horizontal scroll.
- Font sizes: fighter names 15px, stats 13px, labels 11px.
- Colour palette: neutral background, blue (#3B82F6) for fighter A, red (#EF4444) for fighter B, muted grey for labels.
- Skeleton loaders for event detail fetch (3 placeholder fight rows).

