## State Management
- Use React `useState` for accordion open/close state (array of open event IDs).
- Use React Query (`useQuery`) or SWR for data fetching with caching — avoids re-fetching on re-expand.
- Fight row expand state: local `useState` per `FightCard` component (array of expanded fight IDs).

---

## Accessibility
- `aria-expanded` on accordion triggers.
- `role="button"` and `tabIndex={0}` on fight rows with keyboard `Enter`/`Space` support.
- Colour is not the only differentiator — include percentage text alongside bars.
- `aria-label` on probability bar: "Fighter A 68%, Fighter B 32%".
